Overview

Doc_QA is an AI-powered system that allows users to upload documents and ask natural language questions to extract relevant information instantly.
Instead of manually searching through large files, the system understands context and provides precise answers.

✨ Features
📄 Upload and process documents (PDF, TXT, etc.)
🤖 Ask questions in natural language
🔍 Context-aware answer extraction
⚡ Fast retrieval using embeddings
🧠 Supports large documents efficiently

Tech Stack
Python
LangChain
OpenAI / LLM APIs
FAISS / Vector Database
Streamlit / Flask (Frontend/UI)
PyPDF / Document Loaders

How It Works
📥 Upload document
✂️ Split text into chunks
🔢 Convert text into embeddings
🗄️ Store embeddings in vector database
❓ User asks a question
🔍 Relevant chunks are retrieved
🤖 LLM generates accurate answer
